# Video-to-Website Skill

Transform any video into a premium scroll-driven animated website with GSAP, canvas frame rendering, and layered animation choreography.

## What This Skill Does

This skill guides you through building interactive websites where:
- Video frames play back as users scroll
- Multiple animation types work together (fade, slide, scale, clip-reveal, etc.)
- Canvas renders frames at the center while text content slides in from the sides
- Smooth scroll experience with Lenis
- Counter animations, marquee text, dark overlays, and persistent CTAs

