## Animation Types Available

| Type | Entrance Style | Use Case |
|------|---|---|
| `fade-up` | Vertical entrance with opacity | General feature sections |
| `slide-left` | Slides in from left | Right-aligned content |
| `slide-right` | Slides in from right | Left-aligned content |
| `scale-up` | Scales from center | Important highlights |
| `rotate-in` | Rotation + entrance | Dynamic emphasis |
| `stagger-up` | Staggered vertical | Stats, lists |
| `clip-reveal` | Clip-path wipe | Hero transitions |

## Common Customizations

**Change brand colors:**
```css
:root {
  --bg-light: #f5f3f0;
  --bg-dark: #111111;
  --accent: #0066cc;
}
```

**Adjust scroll range (slower/faster):**
```js
const FRAME_SPEED = 1.8;  // 1.8-2.2 range
```

**Change animation timing:**
```js
case "fade-up":
  tl.from(children, { y: 50, opacity: 0, stagger: 0.12, duration: 0.9 });
```

**Adjust section enter/leave points:**
```html
<section data-enter="22" data-leave="38" data-animation="fade-up">
```
(22% and 38% of total scroll height)

## Troubleshooting

**Frames not loading:**
- Must serve via HTTP (use `npx serve .` or python server)
- Check frame file names match pattern `frame_XXXX.webp`

**Choppy scrolling:**
- Reduce frame count (extract at lower fps)
- Increase `scrub` value in ScrollTrigger

**White flashes:**
- Ensure loader doesn't hide until all frames loaded
- Check canvas background color sampling

**Blurry canvas:**
- Canvas must respect `devicePixelRatio` for crisp rendering
- Verify canvas width/height are set before drawing

